title: Most funded Kickstarter projects 2019
yAxis: Funds raised in million U.S. dollars
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Funds raised in million U.S. dollars for 15 number of Kickstarter Projects.
Kickstarter Project Pebble Time (2015) has the highest Funds raised in million U.S. dollars and Shenmue 3 (2015) has the lowest Funds raised in million U.S. dollars.
The difference of Funds raised in million U.S. dollars between the highest and lowest Kickstarter Project is 14.01.

The Funds raised in million U.S. dollars is highest at Kickstarter Project Pebble Time (2015) and lowest at Kickstarter Project Shenmue 3 (2015).
The second highest Funds raised in million U.S. dollars is appeared to be the Kickstarter Project Coolest Cooler (2014).
There is a difference of 14.01 between the maximum Kickstarter Project Pebble Time (2015) and minimum Kickstarter Project Shenmue 3 (2015).

The Kickstarter Project Pebble Time (2015) has the highest Funds raised in million U.S. dollars, followed by Coolest Cooler (2014), and Pebble 2 Time 2 + All-New Pebble Core (2016). Down to the Kickstarter Project Shenmue 3 (2015) which is the lowest.
The Kickstarter Project Shenmue 3 (2015) has 1.99 times less Funds raised in million U.S. dollars than average.
The Funds raised in million U.S. dollars is 153.46 if we add up values of all Kickstarter Projects.
